52
00:03:40,310 --> 00:03:43,439
and the Lord of Xuan Yue City's brother-in-law.

53
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:46,120
What a fool!

54
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:51,460
I put medicine in your bean soup early in the morning.

55
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:53,770
Have a good sleep.

56
00:03:53,770 --> 00:03:57,789
Guan San Mei. I will make you die a horrible death!

57
00:03:57,789 --> 00:04:00,679
Stop talking nonsense. Drag him out.

58
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:07,249
Vice General Zhou. You made a great contribution today.

59
00:04:07,249 --> 00:04:09,180
What reward do you want?

60
00:04:09,180 --> 00:04:10,539
Your Majesty.

61
00:04:10,539 --> 00:04:14,650
I dare not be greedy as long as you keep your promise.

62
00:04:14,650 --> 00:04:16,430
"Promise"?

63
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:23,660
What did I promise you?

64
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:28,620
The position of the general of Mu Xi City and the Lord of Xuan Yue City's brother-in-law.

65
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:31,780
It's easy for you to become the general of Mu Xi City.

66
00:04:31,780 --> 00:04:38,360
But why the Lord of Xuan Yue City's brother-in-law?

67
00:04:39,460 --> 00:04:42,030
Did you forget?

68
00:04:42,030 --> 00:04:44,090
I have Liu Xuan Ming's personal edict.

69
00:04:44,090 --> 00:04:45,900
Show us.

70
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:47,769
- Present the edict!
- Yes.

71
00:04:50,890 --> 00:04:55,199
Liu Xuan Ming betrothed his younger sister, Princess Yun Luo, to me and made me his brother-in-law.

72
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:56,719
Vice General Zhou. Louder.

73
00:04:56,719 --> 00:05:01,380
Let all Mu Xi's ministers hear what is written in it.

74
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:09,009
Liu Xuan Ming personally canonized me as the husband of the princess of Xuan Yue City.

75
00:05:09,009 --> 00:05:10,709
Isn't this a traitor?

76
00:05:10,710 --> 00:05:12,359
You are a traitor.

77
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:15,609
Traitor!

78
00:05:15,609 --> 00:05:17,910
You are shameless with wild ambition.

79
00:05:19,130 --> 00:05:24,739
You are the general of Mu Xi City. How dare you accept Liu Xuan Ming's canonization?

80
00:05:24,739 --> 00:05:26,659
How can soldiers of three armies in Mu Xi City

81
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:30,310
tolerate you, a traitor allying with the enemy and betraying the country?

82
00:05:31,090 --> 00:05:34,520
Since you contributed to Mu Xi City,

83
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:36,510
you are spared a death penalty.

84
00:05:36,510 --> 00:05:39,749
But you will be punished. Someone.

85
00:05:39,749 --> 00:05:41,799
Take him to castrate.

86
00:05:41,799 --> 00:05:43,610
I have an edict.

87
00:05:43,610 --> 00:05:47,009
You told me that yourself. You gave it to me personally.

88
00:05:47,009 --> 00:05:51,960
Don't touch me. I'm General of Mu Xi City and Xuan Yue City Lord's brother-in-law!

89
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:56,899
Let me go. I'm General of Mu Xi City and Xuan Yue City Lord's brother-in-law!

90
00:05:56,899 --> 00:05:58,940
Let me go!

91
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:07,730
I found this roster of bribed ministers in the General's Manor.

92
00:06:16,450 --> 00:06:18,410
It should be fake.

93
00:06:18,410 --> 00:06:19,549
Yes.

94
00:06:19,550 --> 00:06:20,849
Right.

95
00:06:20,850 --> 00:06:22,709
It must be fake.

96
00:06:22,710 --> 00:06:25,010
It's impossible.

97
00:06:25,010 --> 00:06:25,989
It must be fake.

98
00:06:25,990 --> 00:06:29,749
The past cannot be undone, but the future can still be remedied.

99
00:06:29,749 --> 00:06:32,980
The past is the past.

100
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:35,540
Yes, let it go.

101
00:06:39,940 --> 00:06:42,720
But I hope that all of you

102
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:47,300
can work together with me to manage Mu Xi City well,

103
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:53,739
make it prosper and the people healthy and happy!

104
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:58,449
We won't disgrace our mission,

105
00:06:58,449 --> 00:07:03,090
and we'll share the worries of Your Majesty and plead for the people.

106
00:07:05,060 --> 00:07:08,379
She knows we planned all this, and she must be angry right now.

107
00:07:08,379 --> 00:07:13,640
Unexpectedly, as top assassin in the world, you are so afraid of Yun Luo.

108
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:16,380
Yun Luo is no ordinary girl.

109
00:07:16,380 --> 00:07:20,120
How about you blame me for everything?

110
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:22,259
Just say I forced you not to tell her.

111
00:07:22,260 --> 00:07:23,840
No way!

112
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:26,080
That's not what a man will do.

113
00:07:28,100 --> 00:07:29,880
It was San Mei who forced me.

114
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:33,110
I didn't want to lie to you, but she forced me not to tell you.

115
00:07:33,110 --> 00:07:36,150
She said the more people knew it, the more dangerous it would be.

116
00:07:36,150 --> 00:07:38,209
Did you know how much I worried about you?

117
00:07:38,210 --> 00:07:39,259
I do know, I do.

118
00:07:39,260 --> 00:07:41,440
Why did you lie to me?

119
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:47,559
You... you!

120
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:50,180
Tan Rang, what are you doing in the light of day?

121
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:52,460
We are not married yet!

122
00:07:55,630 --> 00:07:59,800
[The top assassin in the world loves Princess Yun Luo, till death do us part.]

123
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:03,960
[The top assassin in the world loves Princess Yun Luo, till death do us part.]

124
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:07,729
I'd like to carve a couplet on your body.

125
00:08:07,730 --> 00:08:11,699
The first line is the "top assassin in the world."

126
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:15,829
For the second line, I'd write, "Please return to Princess Yun Luo."

127
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:18,140
Who carved it for you?

128
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:19,940
It hurts.

129
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:23,330
Who carved it for you?

130
