Well...

131
00:08:28,540 --> 00:08:31,700
[Imperial Decree]

132
00:08:31,700 --> 00:08:35,390
This seems to be Ye Zhao Nan's handwriting.

133
00:08:38,770 --> 00:08:42,120
Why are your eyes swollen?

134
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:45,880
Well... I didn't wash my hands after using the toilet.

135
00:08:48,810 --> 00:08:51,510
Did you tattoo the words on Tan Rang's body?

136
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,229
Your Grace, it was me.

137
00:08:55,229 --> 00:08:58,109
Tan Rang begged His Majesty, but His Majesty ignored him.

138
00:08:58,109 --> 00:09:01,109
So I did him a favor. You can ask Tan Rang.

139
00:09:01,930 --> 00:09:03,689
Tan Rang, say something.

140
