He asked for a tattoo, and you agreed.

141
00:09:05,269 --> 00:09:06,749
If he asked you to die, would you do t?

142
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:09,229
Yun Luo. Don't say that.

143
00:09:10,070 --> 00:09:13,570
You always said I would be first in your heart.

144
00:09:13,570 --> 00:09:17,459
Look at you now. Have you still any place for me in your heart?

145
00:09:17,459 --> 00:09:21,199
And your nonsense is exactly like San Mei's.

146
00:09:21,199 --> 00:09:24,790
You must have been with her long enough to learn her flaws.

147
00:09:29,050 --> 00:09:31,379
You only dare to blame my eldest sister in front of me.

148
00:09:31,379 --> 00:09:34,179
- Do you dare to say it in front of her?
- Why not?

149
00:09:34,179 --> 00:09:37,239
Even if she stood before me now, I would say the same.

150
00:09:37,239 --> 00:09:39,469
