154
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:51,619
I am concerned for her safety. What if anything happens to her?

155
00:09:51,619 --> 00:09:54,800
Enough. I wanted to pick on you two.

156
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:57,040
But I failed.

157
00:10:18,730 --> 00:10:24,140
I didn't expect you to solve the big trouble, Jin Fu, without my help at all.

158
00:10:25,190 --> 00:10:29,320
No way. You wrote so many letters for me.

159
00:10:29,930 --> 00:10:32,469
That hand of yours is even calloused.

160
00:10:32,469 --> 00:10:34,060
It's nothing.

161
00:10:34,060 --> 00:10:37,470
Even without my letters, you could fix Jin Fu.

162
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:44,039
Shang Dynasty women were good at commanding troops and defeated tribes in border regions,

163
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:46,780
which made the country prosperous in the reign of King Wu Ding,

164
00:10:46,780 --> 00:10:50,190
and Zhong Wuyan assisted the government,

165
00:10:50,190 --> 00:10:52,390
which increased prosperity of Qi State.

166
00:10:52,390 --> 00:10:57,739
It can be seen that designing strategies within a command tent

167
00:10:57,739 --> 00:11:00,800
is not only man's specialty.

168
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:04,650
So you don't have to feel ashamed.

169
00:11:05,330 --> 00:11:08,190
I really didn't get used to it at first.

170
00:11:08,190 --> 00:11:11,819
After careful thought, how can wits and courage be related to gender?

171
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:15,499
If you feel jealous that the person you like is better than you,

172
00:11:15,499 --> 00:11:18,790
it will be too rude and unmanly.

173
00:11:18,790 --> 00:11:22,040
A real man should take the strengths of others

174
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:26,000
to offset his own weaknesses and keep improving.

175
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:30,230
Why are you looking at me like this?

176
00:11:30,860 --> 00:11:36,070
I'm also impressed with you.

177
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:45,700
Now, the matter in Mu Xi City has been resolved.

178
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:48,380
Everyone thought you were the real Ye Zhao Nan.

179
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:52,109
Do you want to stay in Mu Xi City or follow me back to Xuan Yue City?

180
00:11:56,770 --> 00:11:58,640
I...

181
00:11:59,660 --> 00:12:02,790
No worries. Answer me after you consider it.

182
00:12:11,220 --> 00:12:13,449
Your Grace. Your Grace.

183
00:12:13,449 --> 00:12:16,379
Sorry, Your Grace. Please spare me.

184
00:12:16,379 --> 00:12:18,729
I am still a virgin. Your Grace.

185
00:12:18,729 --> 00:12:21,659
I did it for the first time. Please forgive me.

186
00:12:21,659 --> 00:12:23,469
Look at what you said.

187
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:26,940
I also did it for the first time.

188
00:12:26,940 --> 00:12:30,639
Your Grace, no! Sorry, Grace. Your Grace.

189
00:12:30,639 --> 00:12:35,300
Let me show how it means that evil leads to evil!

190
00:12:36,300 --> 00:12:40,679
Yi Yang Jun. This is what I carefully prepared to welcome you.

191
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:42,670
How to eat it?

192
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:50,700
The head of the crayfish is not edible. It is poisonous inside.

193
00:12:54,540 --> 00:12:55,970
This...

194
00:12:59,020 --> 00:13:01,120
Peel off the head of it.

195
00:13:01,870 --> 00:13:07,890
The head is delicious and very nourishing.

196
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:18,000
Why are you eating the crayfish's tail?

197
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,480
I leave the best to you.

198
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:30,249
Amazing, amazing.

199
00:13:30,249 --> 00:13:31,870
I told you.

200
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,740
Thank you.

201
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,070
Yi Yang Jun.

202
00:13:52,900 --> 00:13:57,740
I'm really curious when you will give up on San Mei.

203
00:14:01,340 --> 00:14:07,580
Liu Xuan Ming. If one day you find the Guan San Mei you like is not Guan San Mei,

204
00:14:07,580 --> 00:14:11,790
but the person you hate the most, will you still like her?

205
00:14:14,030 --> 00:14:17,510
I think what you should care about right now is not San Mei,

206
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:20,280
but Princess Hui Rou.

207
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,950
Don't you know?

208
00:14:23,710 --> 00:14:26,110
Qian Hui Rou is here.

209
00:14:41,180 --> 00:14:42,660
Is it Hui Rou?

210
00:14:56,410 --> 00:14:59,120
Eunuch Sun. Can you make it?

211
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:02,069
Men can never say no.

212
00:15:02,070 --> 00:15:03,899
I'm old now.

213
00:15:03,900 --> 00:15:07,759
But my great great grandfather was a court physician.

214
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:11,940
I'm sure I can heal his eyes.

215
00:15:12,910 --> 00:15:16,630
Then why did you cover his mouth?

216
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:22,609
I'm not overcharging you. It's a better deal for you if I wrap him a little more.

217
00:15:27,130 --> 00:15:30,180
Don't worry. You'll be all right.

218
00:15:32,990 --> 00:15:35,869
Old Guan. Feng Lei. Zhao Jing.

219
00:15:35,869 --> 00:15:39,169
You three accompanied me from Xuan Yue City to Mu Xi.

220
00:15:39,169 --> 00:15:42,320
You've made great achievements.

221
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:46,919
Today, I specially designate you as loyal servants of the inner court.

222
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:51,669
Each of you will be given 500 taels of gold and 200 bolts of silk.

223
00:15:51,669 --> 00:15:54,000
Thank you, Your Majesty.

224
00:15:57,020 --> 00:16:00,600
Your Majesty. I'm getting old.

225
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:04,349
My greatest wish is to accompany my daughter

226
00:16:04,350 --> 00:16:06,940
and fulfill my responsibilities as a father.

227
00:16:06,940 --> 00:16:09,749
Your Majesty. My mother and I were separated so many years.

228
00:16:09,749 --> 00:16:12,950
I also want to spend more time with her.

229
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:22,310
Don't call me that.

230
00:16:22,310 --> 00:16:26,740
I still want you to call me San Mei.

231
00:16:31,190 --> 00:16:33,600
No matter when and where,

232
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:38,740
you will always be my dad and my brothers.

233
00:16:39,550 --> 00:16:44,089
I will give you tokens so you can enter the palace to see me anytime.

234
00:16:44,089 --> 00:16:45,199
- Okay.
- Okay.

235
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:48,220
Zhao Jing. After we leave, San Mei will be left to you.

236
00:16:48,220 --> 00:16:50,320
Take good care of her for us.

237
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:53,520
Right. If anyone dares to bully San Mei, just tell me.

238
00:16:53,520 --> 00:16:55,459
I'll be the first to rush over to deal with him.

239
00:16:55,459 --> 00:16:59,749
Don't worry. With me here, no one dares to bully San Mei.

240
00:17:07,450 --> 00:17:09,920
My adoptive father had the world back then,

241
00:17:11,300 --> 00:17:14,260
but he ended up in a miserable state at his death.

242
00:17:14,260 --> 00:17:19,800
My father was calling your name all the time before he died.

243
00:17:20,710 --> 00:17:26,160
Maybe his biggest regret is not being able to see you for the last time.

244
00:17:29,170 --> 00:17:31,250
After the death of my father,

245
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:35,650
my elder brothers fought for the throne.

246
00:17:35,650 --> 00:17:38,590
Tian Mu City is not what it used to be,

247
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:41,980
and there is no place for us.

248
00:17:47,190 --> 00:17:52,200
After this battle, I have figured it out.

249
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:58,480
The throne is just passing clouds.

250
00:17:58,480 --> 00:18:02,330
Now I have only you as family.

