00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:00,760
This...

275
00:20:00,760 --> 00:20:03,040
Come on. Drink.

276
00:20:03,040 --> 00:20:04,550
Drink it.

277
00:20:06,330 --> 00:20:09,250
Brother Zhao. Brother Zhao, what's wrong?

278
00:20:09,250 --> 00:20:13,340
Brother Zhao, what's wrong? Brother Zhao!

279
00:20:13,340 --> 00:20:15,520
Liu Xuan Ming.

280
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:18,270
There is one thing I want to tell you.

281
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:21,790
Actually, I am not Guan San Mei.

282
00:20:21,790 --> 00:20:25,330
I am whom you hate the most, the lord of Mu Xi City,

283
00:20:25,330 --> 00:20:28,790
Ye Zhao Nan.

284
00:20:33,300 --> 00:20:37,800
Would it be way too direct? Should I change to a more tactful way?

285
00:20:37,800 --> 00:20:40,090
Liu Xuan Ming, do you want a surprise?

286
00:20:40,090 --> 00:20:43,380
A big surprise!

287
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:49,390
- Yi Yang Jun.
