but you can't keep her by San Mei's side.

308
00:22:52,260 --> 00:22:54,590
That's the only way.

309
00:22:57,210 --> 00:22:59,970
I was adopted as a child by Lord Yang.

310
00:22:59,970 --> 00:23:01,720
