324
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:32,450
Baby, I miss you so much. I haven't seen you for such a long time.

325
00:24:32,450 --> 00:24:35,250
Why didn't you dress up as a man?

326
00:24:35,250 --> 00:24:37,299
