337
00:25:17,900 --> 00:25:20,810
Almost the same.

338
00:25:20,810 --> 00:25:24,370
From today onward, you are the lord of Mu Xi City,

339
00:25:24,370 --> 00:25:28,360
Ye Zhao Nan.

340
00:25:28,360 --> 00:25:32,340
It seems this old eunuch got bribed by Jin Fu as well. Even he didn't suspect you.

341
00:25:32,340 --> 00:25:35,109
