344
00:25:40,060 --> 00:25:43,130
I'm the lord of Mu Xi City,

345
00:25:43,130 --> 00:25:46,570
Ye Zhao Nan!

346
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:59,370
Princess Hui Rou.

347
00:26:05,520 --> 00:26:10,510
Don't worry. I saw with my own eyes that the man entered Lord Ye's room.

348
00:26:10,510 --> 00:26:12,290
Really.

349
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,840
Thank you.

350
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:23,730
Liu Xuan Ming.

